replies.body: I'd be down, play mostly Olaf/Maokai. Only Silver 2 but with a decent winrate. If you are strictly looking for gold players, then nvm lol.

I have a discord community set up so you can find people to play ranked with. I have people organized by role mained, and if you click their name it has their elo.

If you don't have discord, just paste this link into your browser :) https://discord.gg/011amLs7jFpoTjrKQ

I hope you come <3
